      "Designing with Geosynthetics", 4th edition
        Prentice Hall, New Jersey, USA
[T2] Jewell, R.A.
      "Soil Reinforcement with Geotextiles"
        Special Publication No. 123, CIRIA, Thomas Telford. London, UK, 1996

